Paper: hep-th/0012036

Date: 2000-12-05

Title: Generalized geometries and kinematics for Quantum Gravity

Authors: M. Botta Cantcheff (CBPF, Rio de Janeiro -Brazil-)

Comments: 11 pages

Our proposal here is to set up the conceptual framework for an eventual{Theory of Everything}.We formulate the arena -language- to build up {\it any} QG. In particular, weshow how the objects of fundamental theories, such as p-branes (strings, loopsand others) could be posed in this language.